name: Egotistical Ape
text:
Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set.
This card can only be Special Summoned by sending 1 Beast-Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard. When this card is Special Summoned this way, you can activate 1 of these effects:
● Increase the Level of this card by the Level of the Beast-Type monster.
● Decrease the Level of this card by the Level of the Beast-Type monster.
